Global Finances - decentralized cryptocurrency crowdfunding platform  It is a platform for placing own business-project to show advantages to investors and collect investments. It is a payment gateway which let you easily transfer tokens inside a system to other users and exchange a BITCOIN or ETHEREUM cryptocurrency This is a system of accounting for investments and accrual of percent to investors. It is a peculiar smart-contract Â«EthereumÂ» - the result of great cooperation which provides accrual of tokens GFXT(ERC20) to investors who invest their resources in a startup. It is a mobile banking It is an internal exchange of tokens transfer It is a thousands of online and offline resources which accepts tokens as a payment It is an interface API for GF developers        A main information about the ICO Global Finances Official project web-site - https://globalfinances.io Token`s price at the moment pre-ico - $0.75 Token`s price in the basic pre-ico - $1-$1.4 A term of a sale â€“ 10 weeks The economics model of token is deflationary (a fixed number of emitted tokens) Tokens increase after ICO is impossible.
